Class RegionServerProcedureManagerHost

java.lang.Object
org.apache.hadoop.hbase.procedure.ProcedureManagerHost<RegionServerProcedureManager>
org.apache.hadoop.hbase.procedure.RegionServerProcedureManagerHost
@Private public class RegionServerProcedureManagerHost extends ProcedureManagerHost<RegionServerProcedureManager>
Provides the globally barriered procedure framework and environment for region server oriented operations. HRegionServer interacts with the loaded procedure manager through this class.
